-- Battle Over Wynn Resorts Escalates
-- B y
-- 2012-03-13T12:43:59Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-03-13/battle-over-wynn-resorts-escalates.html
Bloomberg's Betty Liu reports that 
Japanese billionaire Kazuo Okada, saying Wynn Resorts Ltd. is 
run by Chairman  Steve Wynn  as a “personal fiefdom,” is 
challenging the redemption of his own 20 percent stake in the 
company at an $800 million discount. She speaks on Bloomberg 
Television's "In The Loop." (Source: Bloomberg)  Running Time: 00:30
 